position as Assistant Professor beginning September 2008. We are
particularly interested in candidates with specialization in Gaming,
Graphics, and Simulation; Software Engineering; Information Security; or
Bioinformatics.  Cal Poly Pomona is 30 miles east of LA and is one of 23
campuses in the California State University. The department offers an
ABET-accredited BS program and an MS program with 10 tenure-track
faculty and several lecturers.  Qualifications:  Possess, or complete by
September 2008, a Ph.D. in Computer Science or closely related area.
