and ability to work with a diverse student body and multicultural
constituencies.  Be prepared to teach a broad range of courses, and
demonstrate ability to articulate complex subject matter to students at
all educational levels.  Candidates in all areas of Computer Science
will be considered, and are encouraged to apply.  To be included in the
first review, completed applications must be received no later than
November 15, 2007. Contact: Tenure-Track Search Committee, Computer
Science Department, Cal Poly Pomona, Pomona CA 91768.  Email:
